第十八週
Term paper topics
 
課程書目  

第一學期： 

J. Davidson, The Island of Formosa, Past and Present History (Yokohama, 1903).  Taipei reprint 南天1992. 
Johanna Menzel Meskill, A Chinese Pioneer Family: the Lins of Wu-feng 1729-1895 (Princeton, N.J.: Princeton University Press, 1979).
第二學期： 

Ramon H. Myers and Peattie R. Mark eds., The Japanese Colonial Empire, 1895-1945 (Princeton, N.J.: Princeton University Press, 1984). Taipei reprint 南天1984. 
There will be a reader that includes articles about contemporary Taiwan. 
 
